snippet.title: The Abbess Garden - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: The Abbess Garden is a cozy and historical gardening game set in 17th-century France. Play as Agnes, a young peasant tasked to grow plants, find and identify new ones, and decorate the garden. Help the community to discover a spy plot, a lover, court dramas and historical characters.
